target_thickness = [5.0, 4.0, 10.0, 0.544, 0.266]

energy = [5000, 10000, 8000, 400, 200]

# Cutoff Energy Derivation
cutoff_energy = [4.0, 6.22E+19, 6.44E+20, 4.53E+19, 6.83E+19]

# Complete Data Set

    ['aluminium', 5.0, 3000, 500.0, 60.0, 4.088E+18, 166700000000000, 29.0],
    ['gold', 4.0, 7600, 37.827, 2.552, 6.750E+19, 49770000000000, 7.2],
    ['polypropylene', 10.0, 500, 164.43, 4.746, 1.289E+21, 328900000000000, 49.25],
